'Lean on me, Merry lad!' said Pippin. 'Come now! Foot by foot. It's not\par
far.'\par
'Are you going to bury me?' said Merry.\par
'No, indeed!' said Pippin, trying to sound cheerful, though his heart was\par
wrung with fear and pity. 'No, we are going to the Houses of Healing.'\par
