Aragorn with the sons of Elrond, and \'c9omer of Rohan, and Imrahil; and Legolas\par
and Gimli and Peregrin were bidden to go also, so that all the enemies of\par
Mordor should have a witness.\par
They came within cry of the Morannon, and unfurled the banner, and blew\par
upon their trumpets; and the heralds stood out and sent their voices up over\par
the battlement of Mordor.\par
'Come forth!' they cried. 'Let the Lord of the Black Land come forth!\par
