fighting.'\par
'But we may have some to do,' said Sam. 'And there's knives and stray\par
arrows. That Gollum isn't dead, for one thing. I don't like to think of you\par
with naught but a bit of leather between you and a stab in the dark.'\par
'Look here, Sam dear lad,' said Frodo: 'I am tired, weary, I haven't a\par
