the Sun was rising above the eastern shadow, and the south-west wind was\par
blowing. Th\'e9oden lay dying on the Pelennor Fields.\par
As Frodo and Sam stood and gazed, the rim of light spread all along the\par
line of the Ephel D\'faath, and then they saw a shape, moving at a great speed\par
