'Who says there's bad news?' shouted the soldier.\par
'Ar! Who says there isn't?'\par
'That's cursed rebel-talk, and I'll stick you, if you don't shut it down,\par
see?'\par
'All right, all right!' said the tracker. 'I'll say no more and go on\par
