and whining.\par
'Well Saruman!' said Gandalf. 'Where are you going?'\par
'What is that to you?' he answered. 'Will you still order my goings, and\par
are you not content with my ruin?'\par
'You know the answers,' said Gandalf: 'no and no. But in any case the\par
